          Announcing <a href="http://codame.com/artists/kinetech-arts">Kinetech Arts</a>, <a href="http://codame.com/artists/cere-davis">Cere Davis</a>, and 2017 Lumen Prize Winner <a href="http://codame.com/artists/matthias-d-rfelt">Matthias D√∂rfelt</a>.
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding-bottom="30px">
